Editor's note: This livestream is expected to start at 14:00 CAT. Livestream courtesy DStv 403 and you can watch it on DStv Now. JOHANNESBURG - The Inter-Ministerial Committee (IMC) on North West is expected to brief the media on Wednesday following its engagements in the province. The North West has been rocked by violent protests recently, with some calling for Premier Supra Mahumapelo to step down. WATCH: 'Supra has a very strong sangoma' The national government has since moved in and placed the province under administration. The ministers will brief the media after their meetings with all the stakeholders. eNCA